quran[6]{c,v,t}:
  33,1,ae paighambar khuda se drtay rehna aur kafiroon aur mnafqon ka kaha nah maanna. be shak khuda jan-nay wala aur hikmat wala hai
  33,2,aur jo ( kitaab ) tum ko tumahray perwar-digaar ki taraf se wahi ki jati hai usi ki pairwi kiye jana. be shak khuda tumahray sab amlon se khabardaar hai
  33,3,aur khuda par bharosa rakhna. aur khuda hi karsaaz kaafi hai
  33,4,khuda ne kisi aadmi ke pehlu mein do dil nahi banaye. aur nah tumhari aurton ko jin ko tum maa keh baithtay ho tumhari maa banaya aur nah tumahray le پالکوں ko tumahray betay banaya. yeh sab tumahray munh ki baatein hain. aur khuda to sachhi baat farmata hai aur wohi seedha rasta dekhata hai
  33,5,momino! le palikoo ko unn ke ( asli ) bapon ke naam se puraka karo. ke khuda ke nazdeek yahi baat durust hai. agar tum ko unn ke bapon ke naam maloom nah hon to deen mein woh tumahray bhai aur dost hain aur jo baat tum se ghalti se hogayi ho is mein tum par kuch gunah nahi. lekin jo qasad dili se karo ( is par muwakhza hai ) aur khuda bakhsnay wala meharban hai
  33,6,paighambar mominoun par unn ki jaanun se bhi ziyada haq rakhtay hain aur paighambar ki biwiyan unn ki maaen hain. aur rishta daar aapas mein kitaab allah ke roo se musalmanoon aur mhajron se aik dosray ( ke trke ) ke ziyada haqdaar hain. magar yeh ke tum apne doston se ahsaan karna chaho. ( to aur baat hai ). yeh hukum kitaab yani ( quran ) mein likh diya gaya hai
